00079     data->s2_end_time = sum_s2.end_time;

00081   }
00082   else{

00085     data->s2_start_time = 0;

00087     data->drift_time = 0;

00127     {
00128         Pulse pulse = chdata.pulses[pulsenum]; //note: this is a copy!
00129         if(pulsenum == 0)
00130         {
00131             double* integral = chdata.GetIntegralWaveform();
00132             int ratio_samps = (int)(0.02*chdata.sample_rate);

00136                 pulse.ratio1 = (integral[pulse.peak_index+ratio_samps] -

00141                     pulse.integral;
00142                 //pulse.ratio3 = - pulse.peak_amplitude /

00144             }

00153             chdata.s1_full = pulse.npe;
00154             chdata.s1_fixed = -pulse.fixed_int1/chdata.spe_mean;
00155             if (data->pulses_aligned == true || data->channels.size() == 1)
00156             {
00157                 data->s1_full += chdata.s1_full;
00158                 data->s1_fixed += chdata.s1_fixed;

00164                 int s1_90 = chdata.TimeToSample(pulse.start_time+0.09, true);

00166                     chdata.spe_mean;

00168         }

00170         {
00171             //this is s2

00173             chdata.s2_fixed = - pulse.fixed_int2/chdata.spe_mean;
